summary.description:
Today, cooler for the outside temperature (down 2.7°C) and feels like temperature (down 2.6°C), more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 10%), and drier conditions in rainfall (down 0.8 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in light levels (up 10942 lux), cloud levels (up 735 m), and pressure (down 9 mbar).

The past week and month had observable variation in light levels (up 11083 lux), cloud levels (up 1176 m), feels like temperature (up 4.9°C), and outside temperature (up 3.8°C) when compared to today.
